name: $TRRIA
description:
$TRRIA is distributed to the collectors of @rodellwarner's TERRARIA ⚘ series

$TRRIA holders are free to gift, sell, burn, or otherwise distribute $TRRIA as they wish

$TRRIA will never be listed for sale by @rodellwarner

The list of holders of $TRRIA constitutes the population of the TERRARIA ⚘ Community and will function as the registry for airdrops related to TERRARIA ⚘

$TRRIA could have additional utility in the future and could possibly be used as a form of currency for the TERRARIA ⚘ Community, though it is primarily conceived of as a social token for, and as a gift to, the collectors of TERRARIA ⚘

⚘⚘⚘
